Repeater

Allows you to set a command to be executed repeatedly, set 
how often they should be executed, and then start or stop 
it at will.


Load Repeater with
/addon load repeater

Commands:

/repeat set <command>

Sets the command you wish to be repeated. Can also change
the command while running.

/repeat start

Starts executing your set command.

/repeat stop

Stops executing your set command.

/repeat cycle #

Sets how many seconds to wait before executing the next 
repeated command. This is not sensitive to changes in
framerate.